title: Colonization.dmg
description:
Sid Meyer's Colonization for Mac OS X


This is a DOS version of Colonization game wrapped around custom built DOSBox release, so there are no installs, command lines, configurations and whatnot. Just mount, double click and play! Just like Mac is supposed to be!

Tested on Intel Leopard 10.5.5, works like a charm with sound and everything.


Please give feedback if you are using Tiger. Cheers!
